runTestsInIterm2.testRunners.markdownDescription:
Specify what command to use for a specific language or file suffix. Suffixes take precedence over languages.

Example:

```json
[
  {
    "language": "ruby",
    "command": "rspec"
  },
  {
    "suffix": "_test.rb",
    "command": "ruby -Itest"
  }
]
```
